column1: medallion an md5sum of the identifier of the taxi - vehicle bound (Taxi ID)
column2: hack_license an md5sum of the identifier for the taxi license (driver ID)
column3: pickup_datetime time when the passenger(s) were picked up
column4: dropoff_datetime time when the passenger(s) were dropped off
column7: pickup_longitude longitude coordinate of the pickup location
column8: pickup_latitude latitude coordinate of the pickup location
column9: dropoff_longitude longitude coordinate of the drop-off location
column10: dropoff_latitude latitude coordinate of the drop-off location
column11: payment_type the payment method -credit card or cash
column16: tolls_amount bridge and tunnel tolls in dollars
column17: total_amount total paid amount in dollars
